@PanoramaMusic.Api_HostAddress = http://localhost:5102

### Health check
GET {{PanoramaMusic.Api_HostAddress}}/api/health

### Login → capture tokens
# @name login
POST {{PanoramaMusic.Api_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@test.com",
  "password": "Str0ngP@ss!"
}

### Refresh token
POST {{PanoramaMusic.Api_HostAddress}}/api/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "token": "{{login.response.body.refreshToken}}"
}

### Logout
POST {{PanoramaMusic.Api_HostAddress}}/api/auth/logout
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "token": "{{login.response.body.refreshToken}}"
}

### Complete registration
POST {{PanoramaMusic.Api_HostAddress}}/api/auth/complete-registration
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "inviteToken": "some-invite-token",
  "newPassword": "Str0ngP@ss!"
}
